{"body":"While `_dialogSaving` is true, the dialog disables the Save button but the destructive “Remove condition” button remains enabled and `_removeCondition()` doesn’t guard against re-entry. This can trigger multiple concurrent `clear_slot_condition` calls if the user clicks repeatedly. Consider disabling secondary actions while saving and/or early-returning from `_removeCondition()` when `_dialogSaving` is already true.\n","commit_id":"b041bea028c64cd071d953f2c668d1020d49640f","line":970,"path":"ts/slot-card.ts"}
